        "Description": "哈梅特舒心 The Harmette Comfort\r关卡目标：\r*先前的部分目标或击杀条件现已变更\r*穿着你的西装，用事故消灭克里斯蒂·霍华兹\r*穿着你的西装，用事故消灭辛迪·麦肯罗\r*穿着你的西装，用事故消灭佐伊·卡拉韦拉\r*不得制服任何人\rThe Targets:\r*Some previous targets and eliminate conditions are changed now\r*Eliminate Christie Howards in an accident in your suit\r*Eliminate Cindy McEnroe in an accident in your suit\r*Eliminate Zoe Caravella in an accident in your suit\r*No pacifications",
